'''Firefighter Larsson''' is a firefighter at [[SFD Station 19]].

==History==
===Cesium===
Larsson was part of the team that responded to a crash involving spilled cesium. As the call was wrapping up, when Travis declared that he was running for mayor, Larsson congratulated him. ''("[[Crawl Out Through the Fallout]]")''

===Andy's Self Defense Class===
Larsson volunteered for Andy's self defense class to let the participants practice choke holds. ''("[[Twist and Shout]]")''

==Career==
He is a firefighter at [[SFD Station 19]].
